<section class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-via-navy sm:text-4xl">
        Training Agenda
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600">
        A structured approach to mastering strategic conversations and getting executive buy-in.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- M1 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-0 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden bg-via-navy relative">
           <img src="/via-assets/vision.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
           <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-10 h-10 bg-white/90 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-via-navy font-bold text-lg shadow-sm">1</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-via-navy mb-4">Building the Business Case</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            How to convince your C-suite that these conversations are necessary. We'll teach you to make the problem tangible by calculating the <strong>cost of inaction</strong> providing the data you need to get leadership buy-in.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- M2 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-0 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden bg-via-navy relative">
             <img src="/via-assets/alignment.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
            <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-10 h-10 bg-white/90 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-via-navy font-bold text-lg shadow-sm">2</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-via-navy mb-4">The Physiology of Conflict</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Understanding the role of the body and the gut. Why do we avoid tough talks? We'll explore the biological responses that block progress and how to manage them for yourself and others.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- M3 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-0 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden bg-via-navy relative">
            <img src="/via-assets/blueprint.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
            <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-10 h-10 bg-white/90 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-via-navy font-bold text-lg shadow-sm">3</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-via-navy mb-4">The Practical Toolkit</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Master the specific tools to run these meetings: <br/>
            • <strong>Reset:</strong> Breathwork and clearing the mind.<br/>
            • <strong>3F Framework:</strong> Acknowledge and speak.<br/>
            • <strong>Emptying the Bottle:</strong> Letting everyone speak until there's nothing left to say.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
